	<Title>
		Need a desk chair? Try a fitness ball
	</Title>
	<Body>
		&lt;p&gt;Do you work at a desk all day? Consider trading your office chair for a firmly inflated fitness ball. Sitting on a fitness ball encourages good posture and promotes core strength. You&apos;ll also have more freedom to move while you&apos;re seated, which can be helpful if your back hurts after sitting still for too long. You can even use the fitness ball for wall squats or other exercises during the day.&lt;/p&gt;
